sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client / Gateway API Router
    participant Scheduler as llm-d-inference-scheduler
    participant Sidecar as Routing Sidecar<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Allowlist as AllowlistValidator<br/>(SSRF Protection)
    participant Prefiller as Remote Prefiller (vLLM)<br/>dynamic port HTTP(S)
    participant Decoder as Local Decoder (vLLM)<br/>8001/TCP HTTP(S)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 1: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL v2 Protocol)

    Scheduler->>Client: Sets x-prefiller-host-port header
    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Header: x-prefiller-host-port

    alt SSRF Protection Enabled
        Sidecar->>Allowlist: Validate prefiller host
        Allowlist-->>Sidecar: Allowed / 403 Forbidden
    end

    Sidecar->>Prefiller: Forward prefill request<br/>HTTP(S) TLS 1.2+
    Prefiller-->>Sidecar: Response with kv_transfer_params<br/>(block_ids, engine_id, host, port)

    Sidecar->>Decoder: Decode request with kv_transfer_params<br/>HTTP(S)/8001 TLS 1.2+
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streamed token response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Decoder: Flow 2: Direct Decode (No Prefiller Header)

    Client->>Sidecar: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>(no x-prefiller-host-port)
    Sidecar->>Decoder: Passthrough request<br/>HTTP(S)/8001
    Decoder-->>Sidecar: Streamed token response
    Sidecar-->>Client: Streamed response<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Allowlist,K8sAPI: Flow 3: SSRF Protection Allowlist Updates

    loop Every 30s Resync
        Allowlist->>K8sAPI: Watch InferencePool CRs<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Allowlist: InferencePool events<br/>(pod selectors)
        Allowlist->>K8sAPI: Watch Pods matching selectors<br/>HTTPS/443
        K8sAPI-->>Allowlist: Pod events<br/>(IPs, hostnames)
        Note over Allowlist: Update IP/hostname allowlist
    end
